{"tid":2064168,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全城禁聚】港府專家顧問促撤限聚令 惟局長預告放寬粵澳入境","createTime":"2020-06-14T15:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T15:25:44.000Z","uid":68366,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"be788b0437c366957d36d1098fa423e53c2e5a32","tid":2064168,"uid":68366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T15:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NALM2Tk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNALM2Tk.png&h=24960692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港仍間中確診武漢肺炎個案，而限聚令亦一再延長至6月18日。政府專家顧問、中大醫學院呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌認為，沙田瀝源邨祿泉樓感染群組應不再在社區傳播，限聚令可以取消，因為即使禁令繼續，每天巴士站、地鐵站都有大量人流聚集，加上海洋公園復業、書展又即將舉行，禁令意義不大。但他稱，食肆每枱8人的限制，應考慮先放寬至12人；其餘戶外活動的限令，則可逐步解除。惟食物及衞生局局長陳肇始預告，港府將放寬粵澳人士入境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200614/SYLVAPFNIOPTE7Q4IHX7CPYWLQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200614%2FSYLVAPFNIOPTE7Q4IHX7CPYWLQ%2F&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8iWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=6e7fe8d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200614%2FSYLVAPFNIOPTE7Q4IHX7CPYWLQ%2F&h=d21b7c2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200614/SYLVAPFNIOPTE7Q4IHX7CPYWLQ/</a>"},{"pid":"f4d75c053a58e6a276ab74d0ba1c4c64e4b4931a","tid":2064168,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T15:20:09.000Z","msg":"澳狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bcb19eff49857b2ebe1eff1ccd38f8b23928e6f","tid":2064168,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T15:23:59.000Z","msg":"發國呢排出街啲曱甴都唔會再用限聚令搞你，而係直接捉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026ecb66c776f057e71f08cfb55acfdb2d1543e9","tid":2064168,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T15:25:44.000Z","msg":"中国種票可以黎香港投票<br />\n回港黃絲就禁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/